Package quickparse.grammar.symbol

Class Symbol

java.lang.Object
quickparse.grammar.symbol.Symbol
Direct Known Subclasses:
ConstructSymbol, TokenSymbol
public abstract class Symbol
extends java.lang.Object
Defines a grammar symbol. A grammar symbol can identify a construct (i.e., a 'non-terminal' symbol) or a token (i.e., a 'terminal' symbol).
